                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Your servo sketch: sig comes from the controller, 5v/gnd from a battery. Each slot carries a provenance chip naming its source module; a slot whose source is missing renders the sketch's 'Partial!' — CONFIGURATION_NEEDED naming exactly what's absent. Requires the pair view to admit third-party ghost modules, and validatePair() to accept context modules.",
