              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Mirrored outline trees, ports on the interior edges. Connected rows carry the region tint (B2's active highlight) and their ancestor rails turn green, so the engagement path is readable at a glance even in a deep tree. Everything else from the B5 vocabulary carries over: ◉ compatible/unconnected, ○ no counterpart, donut = partially engaged parent, dashed pill = potential connection.",
