              "fill": "$text-2",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Reading: green rails trace the engagement path through each tree — on the left, actuator_port_1's rail is green only along the uart branch (donut parent, power_12v still hollow); on the right, uart connects at its top level, so the asymmetric altitude of the same pill is visible as different depths at each end. Inherited children (tx/rx, sda·scl) show no port of their own — their crossings belong to the bundle detail, expandable per pill.",
